'15\t"Rep below zero, 2nd greet"\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I've heard so many bad things about you.  Why won't you leave me alone?  I want no trouble from you!") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Back again, %02?  I thought you were smarter than that.  I can smell the evil on you.  It makes me hungry!") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "There's a lot of talk about you people and none of it is good.  I can't be seen with you.  Let's go our separate ways, shall we?") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I do not speak to ruffians!  Your reputation is %11, well below my standards.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I grow wrathful thinking about all the negative things the wind whispers about you.  Your reputation is %11!  Not very nice.  Now begone, before my wrath turns to action!") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "The talk about you and your friends is that you are not decent folk, %02.  I, for one, will have nothing to do with you.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Back again, %13?  Is this some sort of challenge?  Have you come to insult me?  Friend %13, I warn you--you're walking a narrow bridge with me, and the chasm is very deep…very deep indeed!") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Still dealing in shadows?  I know you can do better, %02.  Go in peace, and return once you have renounced your evil ways.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "%02? The record is still quite clear:  Your reputation is %11.  Our conversation must end here.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I still think I should arrest you.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "<whispering> I'm still not allowed to speak with you, %02!  Now please go, before I'm seen with you!") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "%02, your reputation is %11.  My instincts tell me to slay you on the spot, but in the interests of charity, I'll give you a chance to redeem yourself by letting you live.  For now.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "It is unseemly for me to be seen talking to criminals like yourselves.  Now get out of my sight!") + '\r\n'
'16\t"Rep above 10, 2nd greet (and I\'m evil)"\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Maybe I didn't tell you before:  I don't like you.  I don't see why the high and mighty would want to talk to a lowlife like me anyway, so go away!") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "My mood grows sour as I contemplate your lack of evil.  I have nothing to say to you.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Oh, back again, huh?  Have you been deputized yet?  Favored by the King?  Well, I'll tell you--Mayors and Kings may welcome your type, but I sure don't.  Watch your back.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Are you talking to me?  Go bother someone else.  I have nothing for you.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Wasn't I rude enough the last time we spoke?  I detest you!  Your angelic faces turn my stomach!  Your innocence nauseates me! Leave!") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "It is a pleasure withholding information from righteous do-gooders like you!  Beg me to reconsider and I might condescend to speak with you.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I am this far--this far from hacking your saintly head from your shoulders!  Leave me while you still can.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "You try my patience, craven one.  I am tempted to experiment with the powers the netherworld has granted me…") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "<sigh> Back again?!?") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I can't believe you're back.  My sword hand is starting to itch…") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Are you soft in the head?  I said go away!  I don't need any good deeds done today.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "You've returned to try my patience, I see.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I still do not quite care for you %02.  Your reputation amongst the common folk is %11, which is a bad business in my book.  ") + '\r\n'
"17\tYou still aren't good enough for me (2nd time)\t" + _x("npc conversation", "I'm simply not impressed.  Your reputation is but %11.  I won't talk to you unless it improves.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "The stories I hear about you are %11, but that isn't good enough.  Be on your way.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Ah, %02.  Until the rumors and gossip about you grow more positive, I don't want to talk to you. ") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Persons of quality are not telling me that you are a person of quality.  Since I only deal with people whose reputations are %12 or better, we have nothing further to talk about.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "%02.  Your reputation suffers.  Prolonged association with the likes of you imperils the purity of my aura.  I don't want to speak with you.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "<sigh>  Though your reputation is at least %11, I promised my mother that I wouldn't talk to people whose reputation wasn't at least %12.  Sorry.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "%13!  Maybe someday I will have something to say to you!  Maybe.  But not until your reputation improves.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "My dear %02.  You must tend to your soul before I can attend to your needs.  Go, and return only when your feet are more firmly on the righteous path.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I will only associate with people who won't embarrass me!  You will.  Maybe if people start telling me your reputation is %12.  Until then…") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I can't talk to you.  I know your reputation is only %11. It must be better.  Orders.  Sorry.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Everyone in my secret cult tells me that you aren't nice enough to be with.  So go get nicer and I'll start talking to you.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Hmm.  %02.  I have sworn an oath to avoid those of ill repute.  Your reputation is %11, which is beneath me.  Perhaps if it improves...") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "My friends all tell me your reputation is %11, %02.  That's not good enough!  Perhaps a good deed or two would make your presence more acceptable to civilized society.") + '\r\n'
"18\tYou still aren't bad enough for me (2nd time)\t" + _x("npc conversation", "Your reputation is just too pure for me.  I don't like it.  It's not right.  Maybe if I heard some more bad gossip about you we could talk.  Until then…") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I can sense goodness upon you, %02.  Bring yourself down to %11, and then return to me.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Look, all my friends are uncertain about trusting you.  Until you do something to earn our faith, something illegal, I just can't be seen with you.  It makes me look bad.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I just can't trust you.  Maybe if your reputation were to fall to %11, or worse we could talk.  <bowing> Until then %10.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Your aura lacks the mottled purple and yellow spots I must see before I am allowed to speak with you.  You must do more evil, %02, before we can safely talk.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Your reputation is only %12!  I can't be seen with you.  Everyone I know would laugh at me!  I only associate with people whose reputation is %11 or worse.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "%13!  You've returned!  Returned with a reputation of %11…Hmmm.  Looks wimpy to me.  Do something to impress me, 'cause I don't associate with the weak, or the helpless.  Until then, take off, eh?") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "%02, your personal darkness is shot through with streaks of light.  I won't have it!  I refuse to deal with the uncommitted, the uncertain, and the weak!  Return to me after you have proven your evil and stained your soul!") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I retain doubts about your commitment to a life on the shady side.  I must hear that your reputation is %12 or less!  Otherwise I can have nothing to do with you!") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I can't talk to you.  I know your reputation is only %11. It must be worse.  Orders.  Sorry.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Your reputation isn't appropriate for my organization, %02, therefore I can't be seen talking to you.  Come back when your reputation has…improved.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "%02, your evil wavers.  More.  More I say!  You need to be at least %12 for me to want to talk to you, so get to work!  ") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I cannot believe you would enter my presence with a reputation of merely %11!  The insult is dire indeed, %10.  Leave, and return when your reputation is %12!") + '\r\n'
'19\tI accept your beg\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Oh, all right.  But I really don't want to be seen with you.  Let's not make this a habit.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Your groveling has touched my heart.  I will talk to you for a moment.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "n/a") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "n/a") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "<sigh> Very well.  But this is it for today!  I don't have time for you.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Fine, but make it quick.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "I suppose I could speak to you for a few minutes.  Hurry up.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "How could I not respond to such a piteous cry for help?  What do you require, %15?") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "n/a") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "n/a") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "n/a") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Hmmm.  All right.  But only because my mood is good.") + '\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Today I will grant your wish. I will speak with you.  Briefly.") + '\r\n'
